cs.LG, cs.NI, cs.AI, cs.SY, cs.IT. 

The paper focuses on developing a user scheduling algorithm for data acquisition in edge learning, which involves both machine learning and communication aspects. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also deals with system-level optimization and control, which suggests a possible fit with cs.SY (Systems and Control) and cs.IT (Information Theory).
